SDG_GOAL__GLOBAL: Strengthen the means of implementation and revitalize the Global Partnership for Sustainable Development
SDG_TARGET__GLOBAL: Promote a universal, rules-based, open, non‐discriminatory and equitable multilateral trading system under the World Trade Organization, including through the conclusion of negotiations under its Doha Development Agenda
